marry Gerald for you?</i>

7
00:00:24,367 --> 00:00:25,633
<i> I won't force you,</i>

8
00:00:25,767 --> 00:00:29,400
<i>and I won't kneel in front
of you to try to help us.</i>

9
00:00:29,533 --> 00:00:31,500
