Pervert!

39
00:02:05,233 --> 00:02:06,067
You're a pervert!

40
00:02:09,433 --> 00:02:11,133
- Help!
- Betsy, open the door!

41
00:02:11,267 --> 00:02:12,200
Betsy!

42
00:02:12,333 --> 00:02:14,300
<i> Betsy!</i>

43
00:02:14,467 --> 00:02:15,600
What's with you?

44
00:02:15,733 --> 00:02:16,967
Betsy, open the door!

45
00:02:17,100 --> 00:02:18,267
Ouch!

46
00:02:18,400 --> 00:02:19,967
What's with you? That's enough!

47
00:02:20,100 --> 00:02:22,533
- Oh my God.
- Stay...

48
00:02:22,667 --> 00:02:23,800
<i> Ouch! What's with you?</i>

49
00:02:23,933 --> 00:02:25,667
- Mister!
- Ouch!

50
00:02:25,800 --> 00:02:27,133
What is it?

51
00:02:27,267 --> 00:02:28,567
What's wrong?

52
00:02:28,700 --> 00:02:29,667
Something's going on inside!

53
00:02:29,800 --> 00:02:31,033
We need to open the door.

54
00:02:31,167 --> 00:02:32,100
- I'll get the key.
- Hurry up, Mister.

55
00:02:32,233 --> 00:02:33,833
Call security! Hurry up!

56
00:02:33,967 --> 00:02:35,133
Betsy!

57
00:02:35,267 --> 00:02:36,000
Open the door!

58
00:02:38,033 --> 00:02:39,167
Don't hurt her!
You're an animal!

59
00:02:39,300 --> 00:02:40,733
Betsy!

60
00:02:40,867 --> 00:02:42,233
Betsy!

61
00:02:49,800 --> 00:02:51,067
- You're an animal!
- My God!

62
00:02:54,267 --> 00:02:55,167
Oh my God.

63
00:02:55,300 --> 00:02:56,900
- Lock that animal up!
- Let me go.

64
00:02:57,033 --> 00:02:57,667
Let me go.

65
00:02:57,800 --> 00:02:58,167
Take him to the police station!

66
00:02:58,300 --> 00:02:58,933
Let me...

67
00:02:59,067 --> 00:03:01,133
- Oh my God, Betsy!
- Betsy.

68
00:03:01,267 --> 00:03:02,467
- Betsy!
- Betsy!

69
00:03:02,600 --> 00:03:03,167
Betsy!

70
00:03:03,300 --> 00:03:04,500
Betsy!

71
00:03:04,633 --> 00:03:06,300
Betsy!

72
00:03:06,433 --> 00:03:08,500
We need to go to the hospital!

73
00:03:08,633 --> 00:03:09,700
Betsy!

74
00:03:09,833 --> 00:03:11,667
Betsy!

75
00:03:11,800 --> 00:03:13,233
Let's hurry up. Come on!

76
00:03:15,267 --> 00:03:16,400
Betsy!

77
00:03:27,833 --> 00:03:29,067
Gerald, how is she?

78
00:03:32,667 --> 00:03:36,967
Betsy has been admitted
inside to be checked.

79
00:03:40,033 --> 00:03:45,300
Gina, did the foreigner force
Betsy to go with him?

80
00:03:50,567 --> 00:03:51,767
No.

81
00:03:51,900 --> 00:03:54,733
She went with the foreigner
of her own free will.

82
00:03:54,900 --> 00:03:57,467
I just followed them.

83
00:03:57,600 --> 00:04:00,133
She said she wanted
to marry the foreigner

84
00:04:00,267 --> 00:04:03,767
